Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:39.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's me, Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:39.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:45.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Today's meeting will proceed as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:49.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna is expected to promote you\Nto a leadership role alongside us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's finally happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've one matter to discuss before the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:59.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes told us about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you really lie about your reasons for joining us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll discuss that today, as well as my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:11.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Trust me. I won't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:14.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do not reveal your identity until I say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we don't tread carefully with the reveal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:24.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna may not forgive the subterfuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:30.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll signal you when the time is right. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:31.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I felt like enjoying a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Eibrad, the Joiner of Hands"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna often read that tome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:48.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you think we will be able to possess\Nthe Philosopher's Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:52.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy, but we'll make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,With my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When the preparations are complete,\NI will send a messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:09.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... This doesn't look like him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hold it, why're you puttin' it like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't make us out to be the bad guys, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We didn't come here to attack humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't speak for the others,\Nbut us imps wanted to be professional about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:39.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You guys might not know,\Nbut the Demon World's full of conflict and war,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and we are sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did you come, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Demon King's experiments accidentally\Nopened a Great Spirit Portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's the hole that connects your world to ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The way was open, so we decided to come take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Heard it was nicer than the Demon World, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Immigration, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:00.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Basically. Plus, we were curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:05.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It ain't easy getting to the Human World\Nfrom the Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:07.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You need lots of catalysts and a lot of mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:10.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get those together and you can hold\Na portal open long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very few of us had ever seen the human world\Nwith the naked eye before all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you wanna see it for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:21.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good, they're not gonna try to kill me\Nwhile they're listening to me talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who cares what I talk about as long as\NI can keep them occupied!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:29.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This world was pretty damn interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But the best part was all the peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which was ended by your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wanted to get along with you guys, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:40.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm through with the Demon World\Nand its endless fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The leaders of the Demon World\Ndo not resolve disputes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:49.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Belial's a shit king! He resolves everything with violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Belial?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:55.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's the ruler of the Demon World.\NHis Majesty, King Belial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That name is present in human records as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:05.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One of our royals or nobles probably popped over\Nto your world back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:08.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's probably the reason\NBelial's name is in your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:17.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shit, they sound totally bored!\NI gotta keep this conversation going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And their sword's so loud! It's scary as shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not boring you, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, your explanation was very informative. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I have no idea what they're thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:33.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I gotta do something, or I'm dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H-hold on! I'm not done talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-walk where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:53.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did Belial open the Great Spirit Portal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We weren't even thinking about invasion at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:04.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All the Demon World's wars are fought over\Nthe limited resources it has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:09.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then Belial opened a portal to\Nan uninhabited island in the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and we started talking about moving over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yet the portal was opened in the center of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that surprised me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:27.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And thanks to those instinct-driven types\Nlike ogres and ghouls attacking humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,we had a war on our hands almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why we freaked out and tried to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:34.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what?! Why's it closing up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:47.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The only beings capable of closing up the Great Spirit\NPortal were high-tier demons or King Belial himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:52.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Their plan from the start was\Nto leave us to die in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:58.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is there a possibility that Belial and these high-tier\Ndemons will try to colonize our world?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:04.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, totally. Don't take this personally,\Nbut you humans are way weaker than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There were probably some spies\Nwho crossed over with us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:13.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and snuck back to the Demon World before the portal\Nclosed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:17.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I bet they're telling Belial all\Nabout you guys right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:22.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Now's the time to assemble your forces\Nand take the human world for your own!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:27.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean, you've gotta know how much\Nmore power we've got over you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:31.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Engaging a single devil requires\Na minimum of a three-man cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:36.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man, it feels weird bein' called a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Devils are the ruling class of the Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:46.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're way more powerful than the rest of us,\Nand boy do they use it to their advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:51.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,High-tier demons look down on us lower-tier demons\Nlike we're the gum on their shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You get why we were so eager to get over here, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I cannot empathize, but I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:02.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You are a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:08.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have no gender, but I was designed\Nto appear masculine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were DESIGNED...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:17.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Welp, guess all I can do now\Nis just wait till someone kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Oh, go to the Human World!\NThe sun's warm and bright, and it's lush and green!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! Everywhere I go it's one giant grey\Ntombstone after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:34.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those high-tier devils can kiss my ass!\NThey should be the ones getting killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm done! Just finish me off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the valuable information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You provided me with valuable information,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:53.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and I am escorting you to\Nthe Containment Squadron rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:02.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Just thinking about how different\Nyou are from the other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, he was acting weird from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:23.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A monster that's neither human nor demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You appear to be a rather understanding devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:34.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will see to it that command finds you\Na residence in the Shinjuku Protection Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:38.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd rather get back to the Demon World if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We have nearly reached\Nthe Containment Squadron rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Better than getting killed, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:58.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, the silence is way more nerve-wracking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:03.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just stay quiet. You're going to live.\NDon't mess that up by saying something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Am I sure about that, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:12.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who knows if this monster will decide to kill me\Ninstead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this silence is killing me!\NI gotta take my mind off all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! Your name! What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have a name, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:38.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You are the first devil to ask me for my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did he just smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:48.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Most everyone born into this world are given a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:53.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And names are a treasure that each person possesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what my father taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your father sounds wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:02.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Telling someone else your name\Nis leaving proof that you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:08.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As long as someone remembers your name,\Nyou'll never be truly dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:12.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There'll always be proof that you were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:16.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's how important sharing your name is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That logic does not compute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:25.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure, fine. No idea why I even started\Ntalking about this anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:30.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Seems like I got him to feel\Nsome sort of connection with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And he seems happy that I asked for his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:39.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If that gets him to smile,\Nthen he's not as different than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nothing, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:47.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just saying that sharing your name's important. Sorry\Nfor the tangent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:52.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm Eibrad. Proud member of the Imps of the Dark Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:59.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am an Anti-Devil Self-Development Bioweapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:05.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Demonhart Series Number 05, DH-05 Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You may call me Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Out of nowhere, devils appeared in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:23.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Twelve bioweapons were made to defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:29.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Unstoppable weapons designed to imitate\Nand eradicate devilkind, the Demonhart Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:39.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We possessed power that surpassed\Nour invaders and unyielding fealty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:43.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We are humanity's fortress, blade, and shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:49.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So the ONLY thing you were made\Nto do was protect humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes. Our sole purpose is to fight\Ndevilkind and protect humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's kinda sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:02.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is it? I feel no exhaustion from my duties,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and even if I did, protecting humanity is far too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a strange creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He is a small devil, an "imp".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:21.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Imps are intelligent, and many can speak\Nand understand human language.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:27.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After hearing reports that an imp was preaching\Ncoexistence in the Roppongi area,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:31.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I headed straight to the scene and took it into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As reports suggested, he was friendly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:39.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and I obtained plenty of useful information from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:45.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But amongst that information, he made some\Nstatements that were incomprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A question, Imp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eibrad! I just gave you my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:54.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eibrad, what did you mean by 'that's kinda sad'?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:02.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It makes my heart hurt when I think\Nabout all the problems you're gonna face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I do not understand your statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:10.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, Leo, your only reason for existing\Nis protecting humanity, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:10.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, so listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:17.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do when the war's over? Captain some\Nroyal guard or some shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:22.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No. I may not ally myself with\Nany one political entity or nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:27.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will remain on standby until another threat\Nto humanity's existence presents itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I figured you'd say as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wanna sit and talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:37.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I suppose. There is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your job's to protect humanity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That only means it lasts for the war between us and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:49.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Once the war's over, you won't have\Na job anymore. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:56.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's correct. If there is no enemy,\Nthen the DH Series has no duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:59.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And won't that just suck?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:05.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You risk your life to win peace for the world,\Nthen end up with no job or place to belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I believe peace to be a desirable outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not for you it ain't! Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Think about the reason you exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The reason I exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When you were born, you already had\Na reason for existing, clearly defined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:27.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that reason's gonna be stripped away from you, and\Nyou'll have to live on anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Horrible and cruel, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like hell it's a threat! I'm worried about your well-being!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A devil is worried about my well-being?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah! So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:52.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, all I'm saying is when the world's finally at peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,for you, it'll be horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:16:02.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'll wonder if the world needs you anymore.\NThat doubt'll slowly open a hole in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:05.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And you said your kind doesn't die of old age, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Correct, we do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Death can be a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:16.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whether or not someone lives a good or bad life,\Nthey all return to the earth in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:25.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even after I am no longer needed to protect humanity\Nand lose my purpose, I will live on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will be whisked away from those wonderful times\Nwhen I knew my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:34.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will be forced to move on,\Nconfused and aimless, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is what you mean to say, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:44.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If another war breaks out,\Nwill I not have my purpose back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:50.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably. With you living forever,\Nyou'll end up saving the world forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Getting back your purpose,\Nthen losing it again, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:59.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're never gonna be able to rest peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I said it's really sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My circumstances could be as he described.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will grow, but on the day I earn my humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:15.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,On the day that the war between human\Nand devilkind is ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I would be born to save the world,\Nyet there would be no place for me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I would be born to save the world,\Nyet yearn for another cataclysm to come forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:34.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There would be a day where I questioned my way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:38.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I did not die in this war before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:40.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You needn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:45.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Devilkind--no, demonkind's war\Nagainst humanity is intensifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I am the weakest of the DH Series\Nweapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The other DH units will likely defeat the demon army,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:18:01.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but if they do not, the probability of my death\Nin battle before I earn my humanity is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're the weakest?! At your power level?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:10.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am. That is why I have been building experience\Nby fighting far from the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The humans sure have outdone\Nthemselves with you guys, sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:20.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you're telling me you don't need to worry\Nabout the future 'cause you're just gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:23.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, so you needn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:26.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I do not think I will suffer as you imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:32.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, alright then. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:34.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here's to hopin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:39.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll be prayin' they kill you before you get too invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have to know I was bein' sarcastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Containment Squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I'm not makin' it home after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll do it! I'll see my bones\Nburied in the human world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll live my whole damn life here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your whole life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll find a way for demons and\Nhumans to live in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll keep asking everyone to put\Ndown their arms and get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:24.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we are unable to send you back to the Demon World,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:30.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,we may need to consider coexistence ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You remember my name now, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:41.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I bridge the gap between our peoples,\Nyou better put up a statue of me and you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, you listenin' to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't work yourself to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:59.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If it hurts too much, get yourself the hell elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If life gets tough, then do what you wanna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:07.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know shit about bioweapons,\Nbut you should live your life the way you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:10.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't get too caught up in this\N'born to protect humanity' shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:24.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If humanity stops needing you, that's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:28.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Find something else to live for and enjoy your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo! I'll remember your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't you forget mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:36.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:50.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He had so much to say,\Nyet I did not understand his words until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I kept them in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:57.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If, on the small chance that life became too painful to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I would do as I wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:05.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I would forget about protecting humanity\Nand get myself the hell elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:08.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well, Eibrad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was June 2060.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:16.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A cold rain fell on the streets of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:36.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I understand now, Eibrad, my wise friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:42.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll use my life the way I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll reveal everything to them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:59.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That my name isn't Onyx, but Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:04.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell them the real reason I joined them.
